OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry. Sunny and then clear spells for
OL,7,FShetland through the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight. Largely cloudy for Orkney
OL,9,Fbut some clearer spells developing at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FIt will stay dry with plenty
OL,13,Fof sunshine on Sunday and winds will
OL,14,Fbe light. Perhaps cloudier across
OL,15,FOrkney at first. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
